# 05-chlorine-analyzer-simulator

Eventually a full auto + Modbus CL17/DR300 simulator (coming when pymodbus stops fighting me).

Right now: total-chlorine training tool 

### DR300_Total_Chlorine_Slider.py
Run it. Drag the slider. Watch the **exact** pink → purple wheel you use every shift.  
Zero install. Teaches a new operator in 30 seconds what used to take 30 minutes and a plastic prop.

More coming (auto mode, Modbus, failure scenarios) 
